   Deposit Insurance: International
     __________________________________________________________________


   International Deposit Insurance icon showing the binding of a legal
   book and legal papers. The FDIC fosters communication and supports
   coordination among deposit insurance agencies around the world.

   International Directory of Deposit Insurers

   Addresses, phone numbers, and website URLs for deposit insurers,
   central banks, and other organizations involved in deposit insurance
   functions in more than 70 countries.

   Deposit Insurance: An Annotated Bibliography

   Citations and abstracts for more than 700 books, journal articles,
   working papers, dissertations, conference proceedings, congressional
   hearings, and government and international agency reports on deposit
   insurance.

   International Guidance on Deposit Insurance

   The FDIC participates in the Financial Stability Forums Working Group
   on Deposit Insurance, which is developing international guidance on
   deposit insurance.
